title: Patty Murray gives $1 million to DSCC
text:
Patty Murray gives $1 million to DSCC
Story Continued Below
Murray, a former two-time Democratic Senatorial Campaign Committee chair, is poised to move up in leadership next year, though she has yet to announce what role she will pursue. And her donation could help in the tight battle for Senate control: Party honchos are practically begging for enough money to run robust TV campaigns in a handful of battleground states.
Politico Magazine
By Austin Sarat and Jonathan Obert
